{"tid":1632092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"突然 林峯結婚","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:26.000Z","uid":117412,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cb05ffb84ac95c7e033aa6720862800b83c4a6","tid":1632092,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】39歲林峯去年3月承認與拍拖5年的吳千語分手一段時間，當時傳他已有新歡，是內地模特兒張馨月。最初林峯將與張馨月的戀情低調處理，之後愈愛愈高調，讓女友融入家中，今年1月還帶張馨月回鄉祭祖見長輩，著到紅噹噹似預演婚禮！到6月傳出林峯向張馨月求婚成功，婚期定於12月8日、林峯40歲生日當天舉行，喜上加喜。<br />\n原來他們上月26日已秘密到婚姻登記處申請註冊結婚，兩人的擬結婚通知書曝光，林峯與張馨月住址同報於薄扶林，張馨月出生日期寫1990年3月6日，現年29歲。不過上月20日張馨月在微博上載朋友為她慶生的照片，當時林峯還冧爆叫她「豬寶寶」，「親愛的豬寶寶，祝你永遠幸福快樂，愛你」。張馨月回覆：「承你吉言！」林峯申請結婚消息曝光後回覆表示：「多謝大家祝福！希望大家給我們多一些空間！謝謝！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20191006/s00016/1570298211658/與張馨月入紙結婚-林峯-多謝大家祝福\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00016%2F1570298211658%2F%E8%88%87%E5%BC%B5%E9%A6%A8%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E7%B4%99%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-%E6%9E%97%E5%B3%AF-%E5%A4%9A%E8%AC%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=59e934fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00016%2F1570298211658%2F%E8%88%87%E5%BC%B5%E9%A6%A8%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E7%B4%99%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-%E6%9E%97%E5%B3%AF-%E5%A4%9A%E8%AC%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F&h=2669a20b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20191006/s00016/1570298211658/與張馨月入紙結婚-林峯-多謝大家祝福</a>"},{"pid":"edad7244e39435fb86d37f55203d4329256715dd","tid":1632092,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d2be50560f800a2a8a330d3531e5ae3207fbdbe","tid":1632092,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"管家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927904234635e68bcd1651f25d77a308cbfb9cbd","tid":1632092,"uid":66547,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"是鳩蛋啦"},{"pid":"d394e46831a22661b3f04fdd952f2349d1a992cb","tid":1632092,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2be50560f800a2a8a330d3531e5ae3207fbdbe","tid":1632092,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"管家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992699eb7fe7f283a0150947ba92cd0fa9d805bd","tid":1632092,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"恭喜🎊🎉🎈🍾️"},{"pid":"2b3e21796e4c55655443b96a5bd11870920540f4","tid":1632092,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7dce780d35c7b351a86cea9f7d6d9336070fb9a","tid":1632092,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"唔想做人了"},{"pid":"212b7ac278e3bbfc4c3e8146ddc1c219de24ab3b","tid":1632092,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"又多個腥香港人"}]}